QuestData.Title: Naval Commander
QuestData.Description: We have come a long way in a short time on this shipyard, $n. Now it's time to run our first naval mission and control the seas of Draenor!$b$bI will need to setup shop from a high vantage point to plan out these seafaring missions. Meet me near the shipyard entrance and we can get started.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Merreck Vonder in your Shipyard and complete a Naval Mission.
QuestData.RewardText: Great work Commander! You are going to make a great captain one day.

Objectives.Objective: Meet Merreck Vonder at your fleet command table
Start a Naval Mission from the Naval Fleet Table
